      <p>We would like to emphasize that this web application can also be used to visualize offline annotation results conducted by using the command-line version. Therefore, the web application provides an offline viewer accepting Bakta’s JSON result files, which are parsed and visualized locally within the browser without sending any data to the server.</p>
